+## OpenAI Codex built-ins (zero config)
+
+After `grok openai login`, Grok automatically adds the built-in
+`openai-codex/*` catalog. No `[model.*]` configuration is needed. Select one
+from Ctrl+M or use the provider/model reference directly:
+
+```
+/model openai-codex/gpt-5.5:xhigh
+```
+
+The provider prefix chooses the ChatGPT OAuth credential and Codex Responses
+backend; the optional `:xhigh` suffix chooses reasoning effort. See
+[Authentication](02-authentication.md#openai-codex-with-a-chatgpt-plan).
+
