+For ChatGPT Plus/Pro OAuth, do **not** configure a key or endpoint manually;
+use the built-in `openai-codex/*` catalog described above. Advanced custom
+entries can opt into the stored OpenAI credential with
+`auth_scheme = "chatgpt_oauth"` and
+`base_url = "https://chatgpt.com/backend-api/codex"`.
